==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Hydrophid
<hw>Hy"dro*phid</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Hydro-</ets>, 1 + Gr. <?/ a small serpent.]</ety>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any sea snake of the genus <gen>Hydrophys</gen>
and allied genera. These snakes are venomous, live upon fishes, and have
a flattened tail for swimming.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Hydrophlorone</ent>⟦br⟧
